#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
#                                     DESCRIPTION
#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
#  _service :
#  Set and control service completion.

#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
#                                        TODO
#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
